    ...                                 C=[[4, 5]], D=2.5)
    >>> AA.shape, BB.shape, CC.shape, DD.shape
    ((2, 2), (2, 1), (1, 2), (1, 1))

    In the following, the missing parameter C is assumed to be an array of zeros
